	(67,1,'2013-10-18 07:09:21','2013-10-18 07:09:21','AG Design Group is a firm believer in giving back to the community. This year AG Design Group is a proud to sponsor the San Francisco Ronald McDonald House.\r\n\r\nThe San Francisco Ronald McDonald House is a charitable organization dedicated to helping critically ill children and their families. The organization provides a home, meals and support to families whose children are receiving treatment in a San Francisco hospital. For many, the incredibly long commute to the city and the high cost of hotels is a huge burden on families trying to remain close to their ailing child. The House aims to keep families healthy and strong.\r\n\r\nIn an effort to aid these families, AG Design Group is a proud donor to the San Francisco Ronald McDonald Home. AG Design Group\'s charitable donation will help over 2,000 families annually.','AG Design Group is a Proud Platinum Sponsor for the 2013 Ronald McDonald House','','publish','open','open','','web-design-san-francisco-rmh-sf-gala-2013','','','2014-07-07 16:40:40','2014-07-07 16:40:40','',0,'http://ag.dev/dev/?p=67',0,'post','',0),
